title: Total vehicles entering Canada in Canada 2016
summary: The Number of Total Canada entering to the Canada begins at a prominent high level , followed by a dramatical drop to reach the lowest point in April , which reduces to a fifth of the beginning point .
Then the Number remains stable with a slight increase to December .
gold: As it 's shown in the graph , the number of vehicles entering Canada during 2016 has been much higher during the summer compared with the other months of the year . In particular , the maximum number of vehicles entering Canada in 2016 has been registered during August . At the same time , the minimum value during February .
